OL,6,FThe conclusions appear to contradict
OL,7,Fwarnings issued by the Health
OL,8,FSecretary Wes Streeting last year, who
OL,9,Fargued that implementing assisted
OL,10,Fdying would divert funds from
OL,11,Felsewhere in the NHS.
OL,13,FThey are broadly in line with a
OL,14,Fsimilar assessment carried out in
OL,15,FScotland, where a separate bill is
OL,16,Falso being considered.
